sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant LLS as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant InlineEval as RagasEvaluatorInline
    participant RemoteEval as RagasEvaluatorRemote
    participant DatasetIO as DatasetIO API<br/>(in-process)
    participant Inference as Inference API<br/>(in-process)
    participant KFP as Kubeflow Pipelines API<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant KFPStep1 as KFP Pod: retrieve_data
    participant KFPStep2 as KFP Pod: run_ragas
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(220, 240, 255)
        Note over Client,Inference: Flow 1: Inline Evaluation
        Client->>LLS: POST /alpha/eval/run-eval<br/>Llama Stack auth
        LLS->>InlineEval: Route to inline provider
        InlineEval->>DatasetIO: Get dataset by ID<br/>(in-process Python API)
        DatasetIO-->>InlineEval: Dataset rows
        InlineEval->>Inference: LLM completions + embeddings<br/>(in-process via wrappers)
        Note over InlineEval: Ragas evaluate()<br/>faithfulness, context_precision,<br/>answer_relevancy, context_recall
        Inference-->>InlineEval: LLM/embedding responses
        InlineEval-->>LLS: EvalResult (scores)
        LLS-->>Client: JSON Response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 220)
        Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: Remote Evaluation via Kubeflow Pipelines
        Client->>LLS: POST /alpha/eval/run-eval<br/>Llama Stack auth
        LLS->>RemoteEval: Route to remote provider
        RemoteEval->>KFP: Health check GET /apis/v2beta1/<br/>Bearer Token
        KFP-->>RemoteEval: 200 OK
        RemoteEval->>KFP: create_run_from_pipeline_func<br/>Bearer Token
        KFP-->>RemoteEval: Run ID

        Note over KFPStep1,KFPStep2: Pipeline executes asynchronously

        KFPStep1->>LLS: GET datasets<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP (no auth)
        LLS-->>KFPStep1: Dataset JSONL
        KFPStep1->>KFPStep2: Pass dataset artifact

        KFPStep2->>LLS: POST completions + embeddings<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP (no auth)
        LLS-->>KFPStep2: LLM/embedding responses
        Note over KFPStep2: Ragas evaluate()
        KFPStep2->>S3: PUT results.jsonl<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP AWS IAM

        Client->>LLS: GET /alpha/eval/job/status
        LLS->>RemoteEval: Check job status
        RemoteEval->>KFP: get_run(run_id)<br/>Bearer Token
        KFP-->>RemoteEval: Run status (SUCCEEDED)

        Client->>LLS: GET /alpha/eval/job/result
        LLS->>RemoteEval: Get results
        RemoteEval->>S3: GET results.jsonl<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP AWS IAM
        S3-->>RemoteEval: Evaluation results JSONL
        RemoteEval-->>LLS: EvalResult (scores)
        LLS-->>Client: JSON Response
    end
